hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n欄桿消失都幾恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會去左邊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf04789c66ecee86f5400d2e582a2eae7678103","tid":1201677,"uid":58667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以做好安全措施踩單車架？<br />\n我見好多單車友都係馬路踩單車"},{"pid":"911d06629b8982d8b6906cfde19354fd3bf58406","tid":1201677,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:33:15.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n德輔道中盤谷銀行大廈到對面香港站出口呢條馬路距離紅綠燈大約100米而且無欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f07f67df2b5db368654b09d178ac5d57c25e0ed","tid":1201677,"uid":14256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1bf04789c66ecee86f5400d2e582a2eae7678103","tid":1201677,"uid":58667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以做好安全措施踩單車架？<br />\n我見好多單車友都係馬路踩單車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"可以，踩單車係合法的。運輸署都好努力提醒香港人踩單車要注意既地方：<br />\n<br />\n1. 小朋友要有家長同意先名你係馬路上踩單車<br />\n<br />\n「兒童在馬路上騎單車，須先徵得父母或監護人同意。<span style=\"color: red;\">未滿 11歲的幼童，必須在成年人陪同下，才可在馬路上騎單車。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n2. 要確保其他道路使用者見到你。最簡單應該靠馬路邊半米，尤其是單線行車時。不過哩d就盡做啦<br />\n<br />\n「單車不易為其他道路使用者看見，如果從單車的前面或後面看去，更難看見單車在路上行駛。從後面看來，單車車身較私家車或其他車輛「窄小」，因此，你必須確保其他道路使用者（包括行人）能看得見你。<br />\n<br />\n騎單車時，應選行其他駕駛人及行人容易看見和預料會有單車出現的路綫。」<br />\n<br />\n「靠近行人路或沿馬路邊（距路邊約半米）行駛。」<br />\n<br />\n3. 不過大家要熟悉踩單車先得喎<br />\n<br />\n「除非能夠安全和純熟地騎單車，並且熟識「道路使用者守則」，以及遵守有關的規則和指示，否則不可以在道路上騎單車。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_4_for_cyclists/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_4_for_cyclists%2Findex.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2yAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=c9639073\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_4_for_cyclists/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"17a69d19e3505aeb095a108be017ddb91a158223","tid":1201677,"uid":14256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"911d06629b8982d8b6906cfde19354fd3bf58406","tid":1201677,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:33:15.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n德輔道中盤谷銀行大廈到對面香港站出口呢條馬路距離紅綠燈大約100米而且無欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"巴打識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e5fb906ae678eefdaa6f785a7fa986f23ce807","tid":1201677,"uid":14256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:09:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a63748b4f5aae5bd4c164c37c632b191012a05c9","tid":1201677,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"大家小心，合法過馬路要緊"},{"pid":"a96ad9a2ff17d3df7cfb0880ee886d602c8c0f73","tid":1201677,"uid":18958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人突然間喺馬路暈咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8fa31823e872cbcbbd363b3553334eb6086d1c","tid":1201677,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a96ad9a2ff17d3df7cfb0880ee886d602c8c0f73","tid":1201677,"uid":18958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人突然間喺馬路暈咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"咁唔舒服就唔好周圍行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e005d4be06a3ce0e8f99811b5bc1d8cbe82ee332","tid":1201677,"uid":66346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:00:11.000Z","msg":"好想做個良好市民跟交通規則過馬路